  "detailed_description": "<strong>Sky Survivors</strong> is an arena shooter roguelite. Choose from a variety of skills, unlock unique characters and weapons. Build «stairway to heaven» — a sky tower, each floor of which gives your character a unique bonus. Create your own overpowered build to survive against hordes of monsters!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331710/extras/5e4a0c40ce8505e1775584b7e5562c0f.webp?t=1701195497\" width=599 height=58 /></span><br>Over 100 different skills will help you create a unique build every run. You can become an elemental mage, a weapon master, or summon magic books to destroy your enemies.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331710/extras/8403857be41e650ed274cb1a50008f55.poster.avif?t=1701195497\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331710/extras/8403857be41e650ed274cb1a50008f55.webm?t=1701195497\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331710/extras/8403857be41e650ed274cb1a50008f55.mp4?t=1701195497\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331710/extras/083e7bb1d7c322e1ea704c9afb79dae5.webp?t=1701195497\" width=574 height=53 /></span><br>Each weapon has its own unique playstyle.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331710/extras/410b3bb072df82ebb94f2e0ea8a2978d.poster.avif?t=1701195497\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331710/extras/410b3bb072df82ebb94f2e0ea8a2978d.webm?t=1701195497\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331710/extras/410b3bb072df82ebb94f2e0ea8a2978d.mp4?t=1701195497\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331710/extras/ed42bec6ced2cfac3e979a26a53853e6.avif?t=1701195497\" width=574 height=93 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Bullet Hell — classic «roguelike». Increased speed of monsters and their projectiles. You and the monsters take more damage.<br></li><li>Deckbuilder — the number of monsters and the amount of experience gained are increased.<br></li><li>Standard Mode — perfect for the first time.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331710/extras/5a408b6afa6e86b9e82b9b5c76217d02.webp?t=1701195497\" width=620 height=61 /></span><br>Build a «stairway to heaven» — floors that grants your character a unique permanent bonus or a powerful temporary buff.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331710/extras/337c4dad6cfdc73823c0c6929d601478.poster.avif?t=1701195497\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331710/extras/337c4dad6cfdc73823c0c6929d601478.webm?t=1701195497\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331710/extras/337c4dad6cfdc73823c0c6929d601478.mp4?t=1701195497\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331710/extras/4e005fc6dde9bb647997fd73cf9d412c.webp?t=1701195497\" width=134 height=35 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Auto-aim mode for gamepads and PC.</h2></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Over 100 different skills to choose from.</h2></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >«Stairway to Heaven» — each floor has its own unique bonuses.</h2></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unique weapons that completely change your playstyle.</h2></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Diverse characters with unique abilities.</h2></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Multiple game modes allow you to choose the playstyle to your liking.</h2></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Sky Survivors</strong> is an arena shooter roguelite. Choose from a variety of skills, unlock unique characters and weapons. Build «stairway to heaven» — a sky tower, each floor of which gives your character a unique bonus. Create your own overpowered build to survive against hordes of monsters!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331710/extras/5e4a0c40ce8505e1775584b7e5562c0f.webp?t=1701195497\" width=599 height=58 /></span><br>Over 100 different skills will help you create a unique build every run. You can become an elemental mage, a weapon master, or summon magic books to destroy your enemies.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331710/extras/8403857be41e650ed274cb1a50008f55.poster.avif?t=1701195497\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331710/extras/8403857be41e650ed274cb1a50008f55.webm?t=1701195497\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331710/extras/8403857be41e650ed274cb1a50008f55.mp4?t=1701195497\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331710/extras/083e7bb1d7c322e1ea704c9afb79dae5.webp?t=1701195497\" width=574 height=53 /></span><br>Each weapon has its own unique playstyle.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331710/extras/410b3bb072df82ebb94f2e0ea8a2978d.poster.avif?t=1701195497\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331710/extras/410b3bb072df82ebb94f2e0ea8a2978d.webm?t=1701195497\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331710/extras/410b3bb072df82ebb94f2e0ea8a2978d.mp4?t=1701195497\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331710/extras/ed42bec6ced2cfac3e979a26a53853e6.avif?t=1701195497\" width=574 height=93 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Bullet Hell — classic «roguelike». Increased speed of monsters and their projectiles. You and the monsters take more damage.<br></li><li>Deckbuilder — the number of monsters and the amount of experience gained are increased.<br></li><li>Standard Mode — perfect for the first time.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331710/extras/5a408b6afa6e86b9e82b9b5c76217d02.webp?t=1701195497\" width=620 height=61 /></span><br>Build a «stairway to heaven» — floors that grants your character a unique permanent bonus or a powerful temporary buff.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331710/extras/337c4dad6cfdc73823c0c6929d601478.poster.avif?t=1701195497\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331710/extras/337c4dad6cfdc73823c0c6929d601478.webm?t=1701195497\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331710/extras/337c4dad6cfdc73823c0c6929d601478.mp4?t=1701195497\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331710/extras/4e005fc6dde9bb647997fd73cf9d412c.webp?t=1701195497\" width=134 height=35 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Auto-aim mode for gamepads and PC.</h2></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Over 100 different skills to choose from.</h2></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >«Stairway to Heaven» — each floor has its own unique bonuses.</h2></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unique weapons that completely change your playstyle.</h2></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Diverse characters with unique abilities.</h2></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Multiple game modes allow you to choose the playstyle to your liking.</h2></li></ul>",
